<HEADLINE> Italy Beat Austria 2-1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
SAINT-DENIS, June 23 (Xinhua) -- Italy edged into the round of
16 after scoring a hard-fought 2-1 victory over Austria in a Group B
match here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
