<HEADLINE> Egyptian FM in Riyadh for Wide-Ranging Talks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 23 (Xinhua) -- Egyptian Foreign Minister Amr
Moussa arrived Saudi capital Riyadh Tuesday for a session of the
Joint Egyptian-Saudi Higher Committee due later in the day.
</P>
<P>
Moussa and his Saudi counterpart Prince Saud Al-Faisal will
co-chair the meeting. Egypt's ambassador to Saudi Arabia Helmi
Bdeir said the talks will focus on ways of promotion of bilateral
