Earlier reports said a preparatory meeting was held to
finalize the agenda for the session of the Joint Higher
Committee. Abu Zaid, Moussa's aid, said they discussed economic,
trade and investment cooperation, bilateral agreements and
protocols.
</P>
<P>
Deals on oil, health and technical cooperation, encouraging
tourism and the establishment of a free trade zone were also
discussed in the preparatory meeting, Abu Zaid said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
