<HEADLINE> Study of Deng Xiaoping Theory Stressed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 24 (Xinhua) -- Leading officials at all levels
were called on today to conscientiously study Deng Xiaoping Theory
and improve their efficiency at Party building because the theory
is crucial to the country's future success.
</P>
<P>
The call was issued by Hu Jintao, member of the Standing
Committee of the Political Bureau of the Central Committee of the
Chinese Communist Party, in a meeting at the Great Hall of People
with nearly 200 officials engaged in theoretical work and Party
building.
</P>
<P>
Hu, also China's vice president, said that China has withstood
all domestic and foreign tests in the nearly 20 years of opening
to the outside world and reform and has made continuous progress
in modernizing the country "basically because of the guidance of
Deng Xiaoping Theory".
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory is and will be the correct guidance for
our new victories at present and in future, he stressed.
</P>
<P>
Hu emphasized the importance of studying Deng's Theory on Party
building, an importance component of the late leader's theory,
saying that it is a development of theories of Marx, Lenin and Mao
Zedong regarding building of the Communist party.
</P>
<P>
The most important to studying Deng Xiaoping Theory is to learn
to master Deng's scientific attitude, creativeness and
revolutionary style in solving new problems cropping up in Party
building with Marxist stand, viewpoints and methods, he said
</P>
</TEXT>
