concentration and determination among the players." said Jacquet.
</P>
<P>
France have already qualify for the top 16 with two wins over
South Africa and Saudi Arabia.
</P>
<P>
Bo Johansson, coach of the Danish team, said"This match against
France will be very interesting. I thought about several line-ups
because we have to get one point to be sure to go the next round."
</P>
<P>
