million shares traded, industrial products 10.403 million shares,
construction 6.340 million shares, trading/services 34.264 million
shares, infrastructure 470,000 shares, finance 13.200 million
shares, hotels 130,000 shares, properties 8.259 million shares,
plantation 2.105 million shares, mining 189,000 shares, trusts
128,000 shares, closed/fund 294,000 shares and loans 5.096
million shares. 
