<HEADLINE> Nanjing to Build Large Container Terminal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, June 24 (Xinhua) -- The Nanjing municipal government
announced here Tuesday that a large container terminal will be
built in Nanjing Port. The project was approved by the State
Council.
</P>
<P>
The terminal at Longtan, the largest of its kind along the
Yangtze River, will be 910 meters long and 36 meters wide and cost
1.98 billion yuan.
</P>
